original_title: Yoshinkan Aikido DVD Box Set #1: Complete Techniques
overview: The Yoshinkan Complete Set of Techniques is regarded as the most complete collection of Aikido techniques on any video set. Techniques are demonstrated by Soke Gozo Shioda and instruction is performed and explained by top Yoshinkan instructors: Tsutomu Chida, Hitoshi Nakano, and Tsuneo Ando. Full English narration.
title: Yoshinkan Aikido DVD Box Set #1: Complete Techniques
